{"tid":127923,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打有留意黎緊個隻Blincam?","createTime":"2017-02-20T12:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T12:09:10.000Z","uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab8b13347c19ee5ae263d7ec01cdc6f5a8b672d","tid":127923,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"上年留意有隻日本研發既Blincam<br />\n用眨眼黎影相<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.blincam.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blincam.co%2F&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a077f286\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.blincam.co/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/blincam7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fblincam7.jpg&h=2040145f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://2.img-dpreview.com/files/p/E~TC4x3S590x0~articles/4089395054/a7e5ee_9ed32145f3454aa59fd197397cd14261-mv2_d_4250_2833_s_4_2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.img-dpreview.com%2Ffiles%2Fp%2FE~TC4x3S590x0~articles%2F4089395054%2Fa7e5ee_9ed32145f3454aa59fd197397cd14261-mv2_d_4250_2833_s_4_2.jpeg&h=9c5a7140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.diyphotography.net/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/blincam.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.diyphotography.net%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fblincam.gif&h=41261504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上就係google glass 度變出黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見佢唔係好貴 如果佢出可能會買黎玩下<br />\n去旅行用可能幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (當然唔會用黎影到靚境)<br />\n但到宜家仲未有消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}